name: Liberty
description: Collaborative Project with Cultural Ambassador of Nigeria Bakare Mubarak. All history of Africa is in one face. Through Art, Artist support Justice and Equality. The topic of prevention of racism as an international emergency has been raised in this picture. % of sales will be donated to Non-Profit Organizations as The Kanu Heart Foundation in Nigeria and https://bridgetoafricaconnection.org This NFT is a digital NFT based on physical art by Artist Vera DG inspired by personality of Bakare Mubarak and inspired by history of Africa
